Installation Instructions
*************************

Relies on VESmail -
git@github.com:vesvault/VESmail.git

In the VESmail project dir
- copy Makefile.win to Makefile, or run configure.bat
- adjust the paths to libVES, openssl and curl
  (download those first if not installed, see README for VESmail)
- nmake libvesmailw.lib (nmake comes with VS)

Put the VESmail-win solution dir in VESmail/app dir (VESmail/app/VESmail-win),
or adjust the paths to includes and libvesmailw accordingly.

Use Visual Studio to build and deploy.
